outputMog_mdl.GROUP_VARIABLES:
OC1 = 0
OC2 = 0
OC3 = 0
OC4 = 0
if (NPER==1) {
	OC1 = 1
}
if (NPER==2) {
	OC2 = 1
}
if (NPER==3) {
	OC3 = 1
}
if (NPER==4) {
	OC4 = 1
}
CL = CLR
V2 = VC
V3 = VP
Q = QB
ALAG1 = ALAG
D1 = DUR
F1 = FR
D2 = 0.5
F2 = 1
KA = KS
K23 = Q/V2
K32 = Q/V3
K = CL/V2
outputMog_mdl.INDIVIDUAL_VARIABLES:
KOUT = POP_KOUT*exp(eta_PPV_KOUT)
        BASE = POP_PRL0_IN_MALE_HV
        if (PAT==1) {
	BASE = POP_PRL0_IN_MALE_PAT
}
        if (SEX==1) {
	BASE = POP_PRL0_IN_FEMALES_PAT
}
        if (STU==101) {
	BASE = POP_PRL0_IN_MALES_STUDY_101
}
        if (STU==101&&SEX==1) {
	BASE = POP_PRL0_IN_FEMALES_STUDY_101
}
        OCBA = OC1*eta_PPV_IOV_IN_PRL0_1+OC2*eta_PPV_IOV_IN_PRL0_2+OC3*eta_PPV_IOV_IN_PRL0_3+OC4*eta_PPV_IOV_IN_PRL0_4
        PRL0 = BASE*exp(eta_PPV_PRL0+OCBA)
        KINB = KOUT*PRL0
        KDA = POP_KDA
        UPDA = POP_UPDA
        F4 = PRL0
        F5 = 10000
        KINM = KINB*(1+F5)
        PI = 3.141593
        DPHS = POP_PHASE_SHIFT_IN_PATIENTS
        AMP1 = POP_AMP*exp(eta_PPV_AMP1)
        PHS1 = POP_PHS1+DPHS*PAT
        AMP2 = POP_AMP2
        PHS2 = POP_PHS2+DPHS*PAT+eta_PPV_PHS2
        KI = POP_KI*exp(eta_PPV_KI)

MODEL_PREDICTION.ODE:
CP = 1000*CENT/V2
            DIU1 = AMP1*cos(2*PI*(T-PHS1)/24)
            DIU2 = AMP2*cos(2*PI*(T-PHS2)/12)
            DIU = DIU1+DIU2
            RSTR = 1
            if (DA>0) {
	RSTR = DA/(1+CP/KI+DA)
}
            KIN = KINM*(1-RSTR)+KINB*DIU
            FEED = 1
            if (PROL>0) {
	FEED = (PROL/PRL0)^UPDA
}
            ABS = ode(deriv = -KA*ABS)
            CENT = ode(deriv = KA*ABS-(K23+K)*CENT+K32*PERI)
            PERI = ode(deriv = K23*CENT-K32*PERI)
            PROL = ode(deriv = KIN-KOUT*PROL)
            DA = ode(deriv = KDA*F5*FEED-KDA*DA)
